<script>
const placeholders = ["Placeholder 1", "Placeholder 2", "Placeholder 3"]; // Add more placeholders as needed
let currentPlaceholderIndex = 0;
const placeholderInput = document.getElementById("search-input")

function changePlaceholder() {
placeholderInput.placeholder = placeholders[currentPlaceholderIndex];
currentPlaceholderIndex = (currentPlaceholderIndex + 1) % placeholders.length;
}

setInterval(changePlaceholder, 1000); // Change placeholder every 1 second (1000 milliseconds)
</script>
